  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bupsya is a desktop sticker featuring a fun mini-game. It acts like a platformer character, hopping across your open windows as it chases the cursor, yet never quite reaching it. What could it be feeling towards the cursor?<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3609150/extras/fdfcb7bd45f40e709515913bd6abfcbe.poster.avif?t=1745128833\" width=766 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3609150/extras/fdfcb7bd45f40e709515913bd6abfcbe.webm?t=1745128833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3609150/extras/fdfcb7bd45f40e709515913bd6abfcbe.mp4?t=1745128833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Bupsya escape from Gun Gurda, a system that has mistakenly identified Bupsya as a virus. Arrange your windows strategically to help Bupsya evade Gun Gurda's deadly attacks. <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3609150/extras/3bcf043c69640c85ae2cbbbe0576824e.poster.avif?t=1745128833\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3609150/extras/3bcf043c69640c85ae2cbbbe0576824e.webm?t=1745128833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3609150/extras/3bcf043c69640c85ae2cbbbe0576824e.mp4?t=1745128833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set up the application in the system tray. <br> </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bupsya is a desktop sticker featuring a fun mini-game. It acts like a platformer character, hopping across your open windows as it chases the cursor, yet never quite reaching it. What could it be feeling towards the cursor?<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3609150/extras/fdfcb7bd45f40e709515913bd6abfcbe.poster.avif?t=1745128833\" width=766 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3609150/extras/fdfcb7bd45f40e709515913bd6abfcbe.webm?t=1745128833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3609150/extras/fdfcb7bd45f40e709515913bd6abfcbe.mp4?t=1745128833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Bupsya escape from Gun Gurda, a system that has mistakenly identified Bupsya as a virus. Arrange your windows strategically to help Bupsya evade Gun Gurda's deadly attacks. <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3609150/extras/3bcf043c69640c85ae2cbbbe0576824e.poster.avif?t=1745128833\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3609150/extras/3bcf043c69640c85ae2cbbbe0576824e.webm?t=1745128833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3609150/extras/3bcf043c69640c85ae2cbbbe0576824e.mp4?t=1745128833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set up the application in the system tray. <br> </p>",
